{"tid":1109670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"許志安七點鐘新聞稿流出!!!","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T11:21:47.000Z","uid":132380,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"451042790a52a8e6ed8009d44d483eb640559cf5","tid":1109670,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n對唔住, 雖然我哋係飲醉咗酒, 但係我承認我喺醉酒之下嘅行為的而且確係傷害到我最愛嘅太太, 雖然嗰日我哋兩個都太醉所以做出有少少不理智行為, 但係我哋都願意承擔所有責任<br />\n<br />\n希望喺未來嘅日子, 我會盡力去彌補, 希望我最愛嘅太太原諒我呢一次一時酒醉嘅錯誤<br />\n<br />\n而因為呢件事我會冇限期退出娛樂圈, 以後有關一方面嘅嘢我唔會再回應亦都衷心祝福馬國明黃心穎幸福<br />\n<br />\n而我同我太太嘅關係亦都唔會回應因為呢個係我哋兩個之間嘅事"},{"pid":"ad37a89db0a7d39c43fdc67eee852b0ee65aabac","tid":1109670,"uid":144762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"其實所有事都係我朋友蔡一智做<br />\n你哋講還講<br />\n希望大家唔好誤會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a538b39720b76be44fc574de222d8c63db4595","tid":1109670,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"real唔real呀"},{"pid":"0775de38abbb8795cceb4d6aecb7e571de15c8f1","tid":1109670,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1a538b39720b76be44fc574de222d8c63db4595","tid":1109670,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"real唔real呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"9uppper都好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f603f8ffc60c3a1e71eb1b06847ce2d92e62e98b","tid":1109670,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6